docs: Update documentation for v0.2.0 release

Documentation updates:
- README.md: Added "What's New in v0.2.0" section with badges
- CHANGELOG.md: Complete v0.2.0 changelog with all features
- IMPROVEMENTS.md: Consolidated guide for all v0.2.0 improvements
- __init__.py: Version bump to 0.2.0

Features documented:
- Phase 1: Stability (idempotency, validation, retry, metrics)
- Phase 2: Observability (logging, health, replay, Prometheus)
- Phase 3: Security (RBAC, encryption, audit, secrets)

All changes backward compatible. 73 tests passing.
